The President of the company sends out emails starting with this sentence: If you recall you previously reached out to my company regarding business financing. As per the conversation you gave me your email address to contact you as this was your preferred way of communication.

It never ceases to amaze me how these NY salesman lie. He starts out lying and assumes everyone is so stupid or desperate that they will ignore it. The guy is an LSOS. #Disrespectful #Liar
